data.title: Fictional Life Forms
data.meta_description: Closeness - Free ebook download as Text File (.txt), PDF File (.pdf) or read book online for free. The document contains the names of 443 characters from Marvel comics listed numerically from 1 to 443. It provides the name of each character on a new line with their number serving as an identifier. The characters range from well-known superheroes like Hulk, Spider-Man, and Magneto to lesser known characters from the Marvel universe.
